#. sect.csv: SECT_10_DESC
msgid "SECT_10_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Soul-Seizing Sound Sect occupies Echo Valley, where qin towers, drum stages,"
" testing corridors, and soul-harvesting array fields spread with the "
"mountain slope. When valley winds rise, even the faintest string note can "
"swell into a lethal, spirit-rending strike. The sect is divided among "
"illusion sound, killing sound, and soul-settling branches, and its disciples"
" study not only musical theory and techniques but also rhythm, breath, "
"emotional guidance, and spiritual control. It appears elegant on the "
"surface, yet the atmosphere is dangerously tense, and what is most "
"frightening here is often not open anger, but a gentle melody falling at "
"just the right moment."

#. sect.csv: SECT_10_NAME
msgid "SECT_10_NAME"
msgstr "Soul-Seizing Sound Sect"

#. sect.csv: SECT_10_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_10_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You may bewitch enemies, but you must never lose control and soul-snare "
"fellow disciples or damage the sect's foundations; those who disgrace the "
"sect and still refuse restraint will be expelled."

#. sect.csv: SECT_11_DESC
msgid "SECT_11_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Heavenly Deduction Sect stands in Mizhongtian, where a single peak conceals "
"countless folded spaces layered with the Heaven-Deduction Platform, Ten-"
"Thousand-Array Gallery, formation testing valley, and geomantic wells. A "
"disciple who does not understand array maps may fail even to find the way "
"home. Its branches include heavenly deduction, earth-vein arrays, artifact "
"arrays, and defensive formations, and everyone has grown used to speaking "
"through deduction results, whether laying a small formation or reshaping an "
"entire landscape. The sect attracts minds obsessed with structure and law, "
"and it often produces cold array masters who treat human affairs as "
"variables to be calculated."

#. sect.csv: SECT_11_NAME
msgid "SECT_11_NAME"
msgstr "Heavenly Deduction Sect"

#. sect.csv: SECT_11_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_11_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You must not use arrays to bring disaster upon mortal cities or cause "
"backlash upon fellow disciples; if you fall into evil and still refuse to "
"repent, you will be expelled from the sect."

#. sect.csv: SECT_12_DESC
msgid "SECT_12_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Everlasting Bright Palace lies in the Aurora Heaven of the far northern "
"eternal night, where the Hall of Lasting Light, sacred flame altars, marrow-"
"cleansing pools, and radiant training grounds stand forever lit by the "
"aurora. Ice and fire coexist there, giving the entire palace city an almost "
"miraculous dignity. Its cultivators broadly follow the paths of body "
"tempering, life protection, and longevity, valuing weapons and martial "
"discipline alongside medicinal baths, secret arts, and insight into the "
"source of life itself. The palace reveres light, endurance, and constancy, "
"and its people often bear immense discipline and responsibility, even to the"
" point of burning themselves out in silence."

#. sect.csv: SECT_12_NAME
msgid "SECT_12_NAME"
msgstr "Everlasting Bright Palace"

#. sect.csv: SECT_12_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_12_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You must not harm mortals for Body Tempering or stain the orthodox path of "
"light; if you descend into evil cultivation and remain incorrigible, you "
"will be expelled from the palace."

#. sect.csv: SECT_13_DESC
msgid "SECT_13_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Haoran Academy stands within the Forest of Sages, where lecture halls, the "
"Hall of Clear Law, stele libraries, and heart-questioning stone paths spread"
" beneath the trees. Even before the morning bell, the sound of reading "
"already rises through the woods, and the disciples who pass by tend to be "
"neatly robed and measured in speech. Its traditions include classical study,"
" legal reasoning, governance, and literary cultivation; scholars here do "
"more than read and nourish qi, for they also debate policy, refine conduct, "
"and teach future generations. The academy values integrity, reputation, and "
"the transmission of teacherly lineage, producing both noble-minded gentlemen"
" and stubborn figures unwilling to bend."

#. sect.csv: SECT_13_NAME
msgid "SECT_13_NAME"
msgstr "Haoran Academy"

#. sect.csv: SECT_13_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_13_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You must not deceive masters, oppress the people, or throw yourself into the"
" demonic path; if the evidence is conclusive and you still refuse to repent,"
" you will be expelled from the academy."

#. sect.csv: SECT_14_DESC
msgid "SECT_14_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Rakshasa Blood Sect reigns over the Shura Blood Pool, where blood-river "
"altars, merit halls, bone-refining caves, and essence-seizing platforms run "
"day and night beneath air thick with blood mist, medicine fumes, and rust. "
"Its internal paths broadly include blood battle, sacrificial cultivation, "
"plunder, and body tempering, and resources are distributed directly by "
"battle results, offerings, and personal notoriety. The strong can rise with "
"terrifying speed, while the weak are swallowed just as quickly. It is a "
"place devoted to the most naked order of power, where cruelty is ordinary "
"and empty words mean less than strength proven in blood."

#. sect.csv: SECT_14_NAME
msgid "SECT_14_NAME"
msgstr "Rakshasa Blood Sect"

#. sect.csv: SECT_14_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_14_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You may fight and plunder, but you must never betray the Blood Sect, "
"embezzle spoils, or use vile arts against your own sect; anyone who violates"
" this grave prohibition will be expelled."

#. sect.csv: SECT_1_DESC
msgid "SECT_1_DESC"
msgstr ""
"The High Heaven Sword Sect stands among the peaks of Jueyun, where mountain "
"gates, sword pavilions, and testing platforms rise tier by tier under year-"
"round astral gales. Within the sect, the paths of sword control, thunder "
"sword, and sword nurturing stand side by side, and disciples climb the "
"cliffs at dawn and dusk to seek insight before the sword steles. It is a "
"place that worships sharpness and purity, prizes reputation and personal "
"enlightenment alike, and produces both meteoric prodigies and lonely talents"
" trapped by obsession."

#. sect.csv: SECT_1_NAME
msgid "SECT_1_NAME"
msgstr "High Heaven Sword Sect"

#. sect.csv: SECT_1_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_1_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You must not collude with evil or massacre the innocent; if you fall into "
"the demonic path and still refuse correction after repeated admonition, you "
"will be expelled from the mountain gate."

#. sect.csv: SECT_2_DESC
msgid "SECT_2_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Ten Thousand Beasts Mountain lies deep within the Hundred-Thousand "
"Mountains, where ninety-nine layered grotto-heavens confine a vast menagerie"
" ranging from low-grade spirit beasts to murderous demon kings. Beast pens, "
"blood-feeding grounds, and spirit-binding altars never truly fall silent. "
"Its disciples usually follow the paths of beast driving, beast breeding, or "
"blood refining; some treat their beasts as companions, while others see them"
" as expendable force. The mountain atmosphere is primal and domineering, "
"teaching disciples to subdue beasts with strength and temper their own "
"survival instincts through the law of the wild."

#. sect.csv: SECT_2_NAME
msgid "SECT_2_NAME"
msgstr "Ten Thousand Beasts Mountain"

#. sect.csv: SECT_2_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_2_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You may fight and kill, but you must not betray the mountain gate, collude "
"with outside enemies, or let your beasts turn against fellow disciples; "
"those who commit this grave taboo will be expelled."

#. sect.csv: SECT_3_DESC
msgid "SECT_3_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Listening Tide Pavilion stands atop the cliffs of Jinghaiya, where halls of "
"frost spirit jade reflect moonlit tides and starlight. Its true treasures "
"are not weapons but the Sea-Watching Jade Wall, tide observatories, and star"
" charts used for celestial deduction. Disciples train in stargazing, "
"listening to the tides, and divination, speaking little while learning to "
"read change from wind, surf, and the subtlest turns of the human heart. The "
"entire pavilion feels cold and distant, as though everyone views the world "
"through mist, producing both detached sages and reclusive souls drawn too "
"deeply into heavenly secrets."

#. sect.csv: SECT_3_NAME
msgid "SECT_3_NAME"
msgstr "Listening Tide Pavilion"

#. sect.csv: SECT_3_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_3_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You must not disturb the pavilion's divinations for personal desire or sell "
"the sect's heavenly secrets; if the offense is especially severe, you will "
"be expelled."

#. sect.csv: SECT_4_DESC
msgid "SECT_4_DESC"
msgstr ""
"The Nine Underworld Springs Dao rules the islands of the Dead Sea, where "
"soul-guiding halls, ferry bridges, corpse vaults, and ghost-lantern "
"corridors stand amid year-round sea fog. To come and go here feels like "
"walking through the seam between life and death. Its branches include soul "
"refining, death ferrying, and yin arts, and disciples cultivate beside dead "
"spirits, corpse puppets, and currents of underworld qi, forming a view of "
"mortality unlike that of ordinary cultivators. The order within is severe "
"and the atmosphere bitterly cold, fostering followers who are quiet, "
"restrained, and frighteningly willing to treat all things as a price to be "
"paid."

#. sect.csv: SECT_4_NAME
msgid "SECT_4_NAME"
msgstr "Nine Underworlds Dao"

#. sect.csv: SECT_4_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_4_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You may cultivate Yin arts, but you must not defy the master's orders or "
"seize souls to harm fellow disciples without authorization; those who break "
"this grave rule will be expelled."

#. sect.csv: SECT_5_DESC
msgid "SECT_5_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Thousand Mechanisms Sect hides in the depths of Qianji Valley. From afar its"
" terraces and halls appear intricate and elegant, yet within them lie "
"mechanism corridors, puppet workshops, poison arsenals, and secret tunnels "
"where every brick may conceal a killing trap. Its disciples broadly divide "
"into mechanism masters, puppet makers, poison specialists, and stealth "
"operatives, all of whom must understand both construction and ambush while "
"learning how to preserve themselves in silence. The sect prizes efficiency, "
"secrecy, and results, so cooperation usually rests on shared benefit, making"
" it a cradle for brilliant schemers and endlessly tense rivalries."

#. sect.csv: SECT_5_NAME
msgid "SECT_5_NAME"
msgstr "Thousand Mechanisms Sect"

#. sect.csv: SECT_5_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_5_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You must not leak secret blueprints of mechanisms or assassinate members of "
"your own sect; if you collude with the righteous path and turn against the "
"sect, you will be expelled."

#. sect.csv: SECT_6_DESC
msgid "SECT_6_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Drunken Dream Pavilion rises within a hidden heaven inside a bustling city, "
"where incense chambers, waterside terraces, music halls, and dream pools "
"connect beneath unending song by day and lantern glow by night. Cultivation "
"here relies on far more than dual cultivation alone; disciples also study "
"incense arts, music, dance, negotiation, and the reading of human moods, "
"often blending charm arts with performance and intelligence work. The "
"pavilion excels at turning mortal desire into cultivation fuel and reading "
"the warmth or chill in every relationship, so its people may become "
"dazzlingly perceptive or lose themselves in the maze between true and false "
"affection."

#. sect.csv: SECT_6_NAME
msgid "SECT_6_NAME"
msgstr "Drunken Dream Pavilion"

#. sect.csv: SECT_6_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_6_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You may indulge in the mortal world, but you must not harvest others to "
"death or betray your masters and ancestors; those who violate this grave "
"precept will be expelled."

#. sect.csv: SECT_7_DESC
msgid "SECT_7_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Sumeru Zen Temple stands on Pudu Island amid the Storm Sea, with the Vajra "
"Pagoda at its heart and demon-quelling halls, bell platforms, austerity "
"cliffs, and medicinal baths set around it. Once the bells begin to ring, the"
" whole island seems held fast by invisible Buddhist light. Its disciples "
"follow the paths of meditation, martial cultivation, or protector practice, "
"studying scriptures and tempering the body while often being sent to guard "
"the sea against fiends and receive those in distress. Though outwardly "
"solemn and austere, the temple is not lifeless, and many monks carry a "
"deeply worldly compassion beneath their iron resolve."

#. sect.csv: SECT_7_NAME
msgid "SECT_7_NAME"
msgstr "Sumeru Zen Temple"

#. sect.csv: SECT_7_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_7_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Killing mortals wantonly, colluding with evil spirits, or harming fellow "
"disciples is strictly forbidden; those guilty of severe offenses who still "
"refuse repentance will be expelled."

#. sect.csv: SECT_8_DESC
msgid "SECT_8_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Shadow Fiend Hall lurks deep within the Shadow Marsh, where hidden towers "
"perch above the canopy and secret passages wind beneath the mire. Shadow "
"cells, stealth grounds, poison miasma pools, and intelligence outposts "
"overlap so completely that outsiders rarely grasp its true shape. Its "
"disciples divide among assassination, escape movement, pursuit, and corpse-"
"handling work, learning from the first day to erase tracks, hide intent, and"
" survive desperate situations. Warmth is scarce here; everyone watches and "
"doubts everyone else, yet that same harshness forges a kind of tacit "
"understanding that only shows itself at the edge of death."

#. sect.csv: SECT_8_NAME
msgid "SECT_8_NAME"
msgstr "Shadow Fiend Hall"

#. sect.csv: SECT_8_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_8_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Assassination is permitted, but backstabbing your own hall or leaking hidden"
" strongholds is not; if you defect to the righteous path and sell out fellow"
" disciples, you will be expelled."

#. sect.csv: SECT_9_DESC
msgid "SECT_9_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Myriad Treasures Alliance is built across the islands of Duobao in the sky, "
"where auction halls, the Thousand-Furnace Tower, cloudship docks, grand "
"vaults, and mercantile houses all connect into a sect that feels more like "
"an immortal city that never closes. Its cultivators practice commerce as "
"seriously as cultivation, dividing into forging, appraisal, shipping, "
"accounts, and foreign trade. Many disciples learn from childhood how to "
"price goods, bargain, draft contracts, and keep trade routes alive. The "
"alliance prizes circulation and efficiency above all, and everyone "
"understands how resources turn into influence, making it more practical, "
"orderly, and reputation-conscious than most sects."

#. sect.csv: SECT_9_NAME
msgid "SECT_9_NAME"
msgstr "Myriad Treasures Alliance"

#. sect.csv: SECT_9_RULE_DESC
msgid "SECT_9_RULE_DESC"
msgstr ""
"You may pursue profit, but you must not embezzle the sect treasury or sell "
"the alliance to the enemy; if the offense is especially vile, you will be "
"expelled."
